     SHORT="ratpoison is a fat free simple window manager"

LONG="
Ratpoison is a simple Window Manager with no fat library dependencies, 
no fancy graphics, no window decorations, and no rodent dependence. 
It is largely modelled after GNU Screen which has done wonders 
in the virtual terminal market.
